		<title>Maggie Anderson (BSS #445)</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/segundo/~3/xL9fecQe20U/</link>
		<comments>http://www.edrants.com/segundo/maggie-anderson-bss-445/#comments</comments>
